87
00:05:44,370 --> 00:05:45,790
Let's cook together.

88
00:05:46,550 --> 00:05:46,840
Yeah.
Sure.

89
00:05:48,050 --> 00:05:50,030
Alright, first we need to go buy the ingredients.

90
00:05:55,020 --> 00:05:56,730
