157
00:09:56,350 --> 00:09:59,130
When you went to get more rice earlier, it was already out.

158
00:10:00,010 --> 00:10:01,110
Oh, really.

159
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,610
By the way, eating 3 bowls of rice is a bit much, don't you think?

160
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,370
No, that's not it.

161
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:06,330
The bowls are so small, so eating that much is totally normal.

162
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:08,290
How come you never gain any weight?

163
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,620
Because I work out.

164
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:14,110
Ah!

165
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:15,980
