172
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:37,750
Ah! No way!

173
00:10:38,210 --> 00:10:41,160
I've been taking really good care of it, you know.

174
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,400
Sorry, sorry.

175
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,590
By the way, are you still hungry?

176
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:48,520
