177
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:49,720
Oh no.

178
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:52,290
You're definitely going to get chubby in the future.

179
00:10:53,050 --> 00:10:55,800
- Chubby.
- Cut it out.

180
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,020
It's really ticklish.

181
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:17,910
If we lived together.

182
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:20,580
Will it feel like this every day?

183
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,780
Huh?

184
00:11:27,230 --> 00:11:28,240
If that's the case...

185
00:11:30,470 --> 00:11:32,020
It sounds like it would be a lot of fun.

186
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:34,780
Right?

187
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:41,740
Ah!

188
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:43,570
I forgot I bought pudding.

189
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:44,520
Do you want some?

190
00:11:45,650 --> 00:11:46,720
Yeah, I do.

191
00:11:47,310 --> 00:11:48,030
Well then...

192
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:49,470
I'll do the dishes.

193
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:50,730
Thank you.

194
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:56,080
That scared me to death.

195
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:24,460
Coffee...

196
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:26,170
Do you want a refill?

197
00:12:29,490 --> 00:12:30,460
