218
00:14:39,610 --> 00:14:40,400
Mashiro?

219
00:14:42,930 --> 00:14:43,750
Sorry.

220
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:45,570
I think I'll just head home today.

221
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:47,830
