224
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,430
I...

225
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:05,670
Did I mess things up?

226
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:17,780
Ah~

227
00:15:18,450 --> 00:15:20,900
What was I doing!

228
00:15:24,210 --> 00:15:25,790
I see.

229
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:29,000
