230
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:30,680
Yeah...

231
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:32,650
So.

232
00:15:32,650 --> 00:15:36,920
You're worried that you might have hurt the other person, aren't you.

233
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,990
