236
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:50,610
If you don't mind, I can listen to you.

237
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:53,430
I'll do everything I can, too.

238
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:56,640
Thank you, both of you.

239
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:57,550
So.

240
00:15:57,800 --> 00:16:00,190
Since that day, Kanade, you guys...

241
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,330
Did it get awkward?

242
00:16:03,050 --> 00:16:03,740
No.

243
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:06,170
