244
00:16:06,290 --> 00:16:07,270
You've worked hard.

245
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,910
I just had level 6 spicy curry at the curry shop earlier.
Ended up with an upset stomach.

246
00:16:11,190 --> 00:16:12,710
But it was really delicious.

247
00:16:12,710 --> 00:16:13,750
Let's go together next time.

248
00:16:18,010 --> 00:16:20,800
We also go out together, just the two of us, on weekends.

249
00:16:20,810 --> 00:16:23,300
Did you also get the T-shirt you wore at the aquarium from there?

250
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,030
Yeah.

251
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:27,260
You don't think it's lame, do you?

252
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:29,000
I never thought that at all.

253
00:16:29,690 --> 00:16:33,290
