254
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:34,430
In that case…

255
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:36,000
Is there a problem?

256
00:16:37,570 --> 00:16:39,160
We've also

257
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:41,750
been to each other's houses several times.

258
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:43,930
Do you want to go see this movie next time?

259
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:46,410
Sure, but this is a sequel, right?

260
00:16:46,770 --> 00:16:47,880
Mashiro, have you seen the first movie?

261
00:16:48,420 --> 00:16:49,310
I haven't seen it.

262
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:52,300
I wonder if it's available on any streaming platforms.

263
00:16:53,560 --> 00:16:54,350
Ah.

264
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:56,800
It's already so late.

265
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,520
Let me walk you to the station.

266
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,350
Yeah.

267
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:30,430
Then let's go.

268
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,550
Huh?

269
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:35,090
Let's go.

270
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:44,680
